<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://babelfish.altavista.com/babelfish/trurl_pagecontent?lp=nl_en&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.euronet.nl/~mjkbeeld/%2F" class="external text" title="http://babelfish.altavista.com/babelfish/trurl_pagecontent?lp=nl_en&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.euronet.nl/~mjkbeeld/%2F" rel="nofollow">Homepage of Dutch M.J. Krabbe foundation web-site translated with</a> <a href="/wiki/Babel_Fish_(website)" title="Babel Fish (website)">Babel Fish</a></li>
</ol>
